@AzureOnyx has chosen the winner for Week #13‚Ä¶

"Simon‚Äôs entry is this week‚Äôs winner. He perfectly uses the Panic Attack soundpack while keeping the sound signature of the overall song. Keeps the energy pumping while greatly using automation. Hard hitting percussion with synth highs while occupying stereo space rather than semi-stereo with more lighter songs. Buildups are leaning towards the generic side of EDM, the inclusion of Lobster from The Future soundpack sounds a bit out of place, but greatly appreciate the attempt of including it in the song. I‚Äôve personally used Lobster in my songs, definitely a hard sound to use, let alone master.

Congrats Simon!
